									<div class="post_tag"><i class="fa fa-tags"></i><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/agriculture/" rel="tag">agriculture</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/dave-hage/" rel="tag">Dave Hage</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/des-moines/" rel="tag">Des Moines</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/environmental-contamination/" rel="tag">environmental contamination</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/farming/" rel="tag">farming</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/iowa/" rel="tag">Iowa</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/josephine-marcotty/" rel="tag">Josephine Marcotty</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/penguin-random-house/" rel="tag">Penguin Random House</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/pollution/" rel="tag">pollution</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/random-house/" rel="tag">Random House</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/rivers/" rel="tag">rivers</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/sea-of-grass-the-conquest-ruin-and-redemption-of-nature-on-the-american-prairie/" rel="tag">Sea of Grass: The Conquest Ruin and Redemption of Nature on the American Prairie</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/the-environment/" rel="tag">the environment</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/the-midwest/" rel="tag">The Midwest</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/water/" rel="tag">water</a><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/water-pollution/" rel="tag">water pollution</a></div>									
																		
